rows.label: tlk47300164_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Everything's the same as always here,
but it's like there's some great invisible
shadow looming. I've got a bad feeling...

rows.label: tlk47300164_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I've heard that Iira are responsible
for terrible wrongdoings, but do they
have anything to gain by coming here?

rows.label: tlk47300164_02_msg0003
rows.name:
There are no soldiers here. We can't
fight them like Superbia. All we can
do now is pray to the Village Guardian...
